---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Resources — Ranking Atlas"
  description="Primary-source research on backlink pricing, AI search visibility, and citation equity for B2B SaaS marketing teams."
>

<section class="py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink leading-[1.1] mb-6">
      Research and Analysis for B2B SaaS Marketing Teams
    </h1>
    <p class="text-body text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
      Primary-source data and strategic analysis on how editorial coverage, AI search systems, and the link-building market are evolving. Published by Ranking Atlas.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-bg-cream">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

    <a href="/resources/ai-search-visibility" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow block">
      <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-brand font-medium mb-3">Guide</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink mb-4 leading-snug group-hover:text-[#5D4FE0] transition-colors">
        AI Search Visibility
      </h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
        How ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google AI Overviews, and Claude choose which brands to mention — and what builds the citation equity that puts you in the answer.
      </p>
      <div class="text-sm text-brand font-medium group-hover:underline">Read the guide →</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/resources/the-cost-of-authority" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow block">
      <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-brand font-medium mb-3">Data Report</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink mb-4 leading-snug group-hover:text-[#5D4FE0] transition-colors">
        The Cost of Authority: 2026 Backlink Pricing Index
      </h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Primary-source pricing data across 140,000+ publisher listings and six years of agency snapshots. What backlinks cost, how pricing has moved 2020–2026, and why the market is solving the wrong problem.
      </p>
      <div class="text-sm text-brand font-medium group-hover:underline">Read the report →</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/resources/citation-equity-vs-link-building" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow block md:col-span-2">
      <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-brand font-medium mb-3">Essay</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink mb-4 leading-snug group-hover:text-[#5D4FE0] transition-colors">
        Citation Equity vs Link Building: Why the Old Playbook Stops Working
      </h2>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Link-building was designed for a search system that no longer exists. Citation equity is what AI systems use to decide which brands to cite. Here's the difference, the evidence, and why one compounds while the other decays.
      </p>
      <div class="text-sm text-brand font-medium group-hover:underline">Read the essay →</div>
    </a>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
